LEGENDARY Jazz artist Thandi Klaasen has died at the age of 86! Her daughter, Lorraine broke the sad news today on her Facebook page stating that Thandi passed away in the early mornings of today.&nbsp;Thandi was a well-known jazz musician from&nbsp; Sophiatown, Gauteng . &nbsp;Lorraine said: &ldquo;Today is the day my Mom left us she passed away this morning peacefully. Thank you all for you're kind words and prayers&nbsp; I use to share this incouraging scripture Revelations 21 verse 2 3 4. In part it says Even Death will be no more.no pain.no suffering it will be things of the past.&nbsp; We will update for funeral arrangement, On behalf of my family, WE THANK YOU ALL.&rdquo; More to follow!